{"tid":2136348,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"明愛值班醫生染疫 成首例  公院失守 團體促增檢測","createTime":"2020-08-02T05:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T12:52:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"418de94427fc039d087e6c42ab812f6e617aed73","tid":2136348,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T05:46:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200802/ERRBI562ALFHE65B7ZSSB6ASDI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200802%2FERRBI562ALFHE65B7ZSSB6ASDI%2F&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAne9tl09raJ%2B2zMWOssuGUT0%3D&h=2dbc456f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200802%2FERRBI562ALFHE65B7ZSSB6ASDI%2F&h=ae145fc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200802/ERRBI562ALFHE65B7ZSSB6ASDI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n明愛值班醫生染疫 成首例 <br />\n公院失守 團體促增檢測<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港首次有工作中的公立醫院醫生感染武漢肺炎，明愛醫院一名內科男醫生昨日初步確診，他病發前一天仍有上班，為病人診症及檢查身體。關注病人權益的團體擔心抗疫前線的公立醫院會失守，一旦越來越多醫護人員確診，就算不引致院內爆發，大批共事的醫護被列為緊密接觸者而需隔離，對人手已緊絀的公共醫療服務亦將構成極大壓力。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局總行政經理何婉霞表示，明。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2vE3LawIPMjE5nUKgPqgH_fhxJM=/640x424/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OU4TVD6NL44J7B3TLTUMPHJ3VM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2vE3LawIPMjE5nUKgPqgH_fhxJM%3D%2F640x424%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOU4TVD6NL44J7B3TLTUMPHJ3VM.jpg&h=1bda2190&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明愛醫院一名內科醫生昨初步確診，有保安員阻擋記者拍攝。&lt;br /&gt;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下班後始知家人中招<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：林鄭懶理制裁 拒談家人擁英籍<br />\n<br />\n被問及為何該醫生家人前日已確診，但他未被隔離檢疫仍可照常上班，何婉霞解釋，醫生家人是前天他下班後晚上才確診，至昨晨醫生也覺得喉嚨痛及不適，於是到急症室求醫，下午檢測結果初步呈陽性。該名內科醫生主要負責照顧住院病人、診症及檢查身體。何婉霞指在一般情況下，若確診者與接觸者都有戴外科口罩，接觸者毋須列為緊密接觸者，只需進行醫學監測。<br />\n<br />\n這是首次有工作中的公立。。。。。。。。。。。。間受感染。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TT4LP3hbCsRnVn5eUxl26ep9lQE=/640x959/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QJKL2YTAQQXZ2MQWNIFZLLAND4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTT4LP3hbCsRnVn5eUxl26ep9lQE%3D%2F640x959%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQJKL2YTAQQXZ2MQWNIFZLLAND4.jpg&h=eb991bcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明愛醫院正追蹤醫生接觸過的病人，暫未知涉及人數。<br />\n<br />\n關注病人權益的社區組織協會幹事彭鴻昌指出，目前社區爆發情況嚴峻，公立。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n瑪麗醫院亦有一名繳費處女文員確診，她主要在本院S座一樓。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屯院病人確診 鄰床須隔離<br />\n<br />\n公立醫院近日發生多宗隱形病人入住普通病房後才確診的個案。屯門醫院一名81歲長期病患男病人昨亦確診，他曾到急症室求醫，並於急症室病房逗留，兩名曾與他同一病格。。。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"3472f5faf00dd86565bc53ce47df1944054a84d9","tid":2136348,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T05:47:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2vE3LawIPMjE5nUKgPqgH_fhxJM%3D/640x424/filters:quality%28100%29/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OU4TVD6NL44J7B3TLTUMPHJ3VM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2vE3LawIPMjE5nUKgPqgH_fhxJM%253D%2F640x424%2Ffilters%3Aquality%2528100%2529%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOU4TVD6NL44J7B3TLTUMPHJ3VM.jpg&h=b0e5ce73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸咁遮鏡頭"},{"pid":"d8e3851ef153b2bace7d5640b9553b080a9669ca","tid":2136348,"uid":181549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T05:50:15.000Z","msg":"「相信並非院內感染」<br />\nHA最仆街 唔肯入工傷"},{"pid":"fd8d8c373a544461aaeb088e7dbaf8441900eab9","tid":2136348,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T05:51:56.000Z","msg":"保安員好撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f86d989ec47224bd5260e8de984d43a5c80c7359","tid":2136348,"uid":162910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T12:15:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7789ae122ed96acd38a2e6067b56961d1d57a4e","tid":2136348,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T12:52:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}